# Project Structure Guide

This is a Gatsby-based website for Castizo Restauraciones, a furniture restoration business in Spain.

## Main Configuration
- [gatsby-config.ts](mdc:gatsby-config.ts): Contains all Gatsby configuration, including plugins, site metadata, and SEO settings.
- [package.json](mdc:package.json): Project dependencies and scripts.

## Content Structure
- [src/data/successCases.ts](mdc:src/data/successCases.ts): Contains case studies of restoration projects with before/after images.

## Components
- [src/components/SEO.tsx](mdc:src/components/SEO.tsx): SEO component with Schema.org JSON-LD structured data.
- [src/components/Layout.tsx](mdc:src/components/Layout.tsx): Main layout component with header, navigation, and footer.

## Pages
- [src/pages/index.tsx](mdc:src/pages/index.tsx): Homepage with main sections.
- [src/pages/contacto.tsx](mdc:src/pages/contacto.tsx): Contact page with business information.
- [src/pages/casos-de-exito.tsx](mdc:src/pages/casos-de-exito.tsx): Success cases/portfolio page.

## Static Assets
- [static/images/](mdc:static/images): Directory containing images used throughout the site.
- [static/robots.txt](mdc:static/robots.txt): SEO configuration for search engine crawlers.
